    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_5856818392788561668.png",
                "id": "talent77722",
                "key": "Cooling Treatment ",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Cooling Treatment "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bitey Shark</span> to self, then enter <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span> and gain 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\"Nightsoul points.\"</span> (This skill cannot be used after the character enters <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>)<br>(Characters with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bitey Shark</span> attached can use the Technique: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sharky Surfboard</span>)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>The character to which this is attached accumulates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\"Nightsoul points.\" </span>(Max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/6eca0515aa0b943ce4863f23e7bac54f_151968521404556529.png",
                "id": "talent13603",
                "key": "Surfshark Wavebreaker ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Surfshark Wavebreaker "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shark Missile</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/de980cad3d9422986776632fa61c2eff_8542295095863356730.png",
                "id": "talent71045",
                "key": "Boomsharka-laka ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Boomsharka-laka "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Equipment Card</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After either side switches characters, and Mualani is the active character:</span> Spend 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul point</span> to apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bite Target</span> to the opposing active character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Technique</span>: Sharky Surfboard<br>When the character to which this is attached has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul points</span>, discard this card. When this card is discarded, the attached character's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span> ends.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4080834498251782027.png",
                "id": "talent78957",
                "key": "Bitey Shark",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/6fc92bf55b26c115eefe4f2a113677e0_1150574838065472507.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Bitey Shark"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Technique</span><br>Switch to your previous character, attach 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bite Target</span> stack to the opposing active character. (If your standby characters have all been defeated, consume 1 extra <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul point</span>)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7123582379862693091.png",
                "id": "talent38020",
                "key": "Sharky Surfboard",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Sharky Surfboard"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usa</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">ge(s): 2</span> (Can stack, no stack limit)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7076510914788104242.png",
                "id": "talent99481",
                "key": "Shark Missile",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/f2ea88f3013a7c33fb47942114373377_2043001924287352310.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Shark Missile"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2548248997917777837.png",
                "id": "talent9476",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Technique</span></strong><br>When the active character is equipped with a Technique card, they can use the corresponding Technique.<br>Using a Technique counts as a Combat Action. If the character is unable to use Skills due to conditions like Frozen, Petrification, or Stun, they are also unable to use the Technique.<br>Using a Technique is not considered as using a Skill. Therefore, it cannot trigger effects such as \"After using a skill\" or \"After the character triggers an Elemental Reaction.\" Damage dealt by using a Technique is not considered Damage dealt by the character.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bite Target</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When receiving damage dealt by Mualani or Shark Missile:</span> Remove this effect. For each stack, increase the damage by 2.<br>(Stacks are accumulative, with no limit.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/07/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3817955532973932413.png",
                "id": "talent3742",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
